<span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>For the inverse hyperbolic cosecant, the principal value is defined as
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle \operatorname {arcsch} z=3D\operatorname {Log} \left({\frac {1}=
{z}}+{\sqrt {{\frac {1}{z^{2}}}+1}}\,\right).}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mi>arcsch</mi>
        <mo>=E2=81=A1<!-- =E2=81=A1 --></mo>
        <mi>z</mi>
        <mo>=3D</mo>
        <mi>Log</mi>
        <mo>=E2=81=A1<!-- =E2=81=A1 --></mo>
        <mrow>
          <mo>(</mo>
          <mrow>
            <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
              <mfrac>
                <mn>1</mn>
                <mi>z</mi>
              </mfrac>
            </mrow>
            <mo>+</mo>
            <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
              <msqrt>
                <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                  <mfrac>
                    <mn>1</mn>
                    <msup>
                      <mi>z</mi>
                      <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
                        <mn>2</mn>
                      </mrow>
                    </msup>
                  </mfrac>
                </mrow>
                <mo>+</mo>
                <mn>1</mn>
              </msqrt>
            </mrow>
            <mspace width=3D"thinmathspace"></mspace>
          </mrow>
          <mo>)</mo>
        </mrow>
        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
